                    <span>Recommend this one.  D'Este is one of my favorite popular history authors and he certainly came through with this one.  Of the many works on Patton I have read, this one seems to catch the soul of the man closer than anyother.  The book is a easy read, comfortable and extremely informative. This is one of those I will reread soon.  Certainly recommend you add this one to your collection.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">The best Patton biography</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
